#FashionStore – React E-Commerce Website

**FashionStore** is a modern **React.js E-Commerce web application** that allows users to browse fashion products, filter by category, add items to a shopping cart, manage product quantities, and view the total price converted from **USD ($) to Indian Rupees (₹)**.

This project demonstrates **React component architecture, state management, API integration, and responsive UI development**.

---

##  Key Features

✔ Modern responsive UI design
✔ Product data fetched from **FakeStore API**
✔ Category filtering (Women, Men, Jewelry, Accessories)
✔ Add products to cart
✔ Increase / Decrease product quantity
✔ Remove products from cart
✔ Real-time cart counter in navigation bar
✔ Automatic cart total calculation
✔ **Currency conversion (USD → INR)**
✔ Email subscription section for offers
✔ Contact form with validation

