##  API Used

Product data is fetched from:

```
https://fakestoreapi.com
```

Endpoints used:

```
/products
/products/categories
/products/category/{category}
```

---

##  Currency Conversion

Product prices from the API are in **USD ($)** and converted to **Indian Rupees (₹)**.

Example logic:

```javascript
const USD_TO_INR = 83;
const priceINR = product.price * USD_TO_INR;
```

