## ⚙️ Installation

Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/fashionstore-react.git
```

Install dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

Run the project

```bash
npm start
```

Application runs on:

```
http://localhost:3000
```

